CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FAs Trump claims the war against Iran
OL,8,Fis nearly over, ITV News Correspondent
OL,9,FJohn Ray, Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,10,FKachroo and US Correspondent Dan
OL,11,FRivers report on the latest
OL,12,Fdevelopments
OL,14,FIran has fired more drones and
OL,15,Fmissiles at Gulf Arab countries, as US
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump sent
OL,17,Fcontradictory signals about how long
OL,18,Fthe war could last.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe Iran war has sent oil prices
OL,8,Fsurging and shocked global economies.
OL,9,FAfter a day in which oil prices rose
OL,10,Fto a four-year high, before falling
OL,11,Fslightly, Trump wrote on his Truth
OL,12,FSocial that Iran will be met with
OL,13,F"Death, Fire and Fury" if Tehran
OL,14,Fprevents the transport of oil across
OL,15,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FIn addition to firing missiles and
OL,8,Fdrones at Israel and at American bases
OL,9,Fin the region, Iran has also been
OL,10,Ftargeting energy infrastructure,
OL,11,Fwhich, combined with its stranglehold
OL,12,Fon the Strait of Hormuz, has sent oil
OL,13,Fprices soaring.
OL,15,FTrump wrote on Truth Social on Monday
OL,16,Fnight that "If Iran does anything that
OL,17,Fstops the flow of Oil within the
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz, they will be hit by
OL,19,Fthe United States of America TWENTY
OL,20,FTIMES HARDER than they have been hit
OL,21,Fthus far."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,F"Additionally, we will take out easily
OL,8,Fdestroyable targets that will make it
OL,9,Fvirtually impossible for Iran to ever
OL,10,Fbe built back, as a Nation, again `
OL,11,FDeath, Fire, and Fury will reign upon
OL,12,Fthem ` But I hope, and pray, that it
OL,13,Fdoes not happen!"
OL,15,FTrump, who has previously said that
OL,16,Fthe war could last for a month or
OL,17,Flonger, on Tuesday sought to downplay
OL,18,Fgrowing fears that it could be a long-
OL,19,Fterm regional conflict, saying the war
OL,20,Fagainst Iran will be over "very soon".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe war began with joint US-Israeli
OL,8,Fattacks on Iran on February 28 and has
OL,9,Fsince escalated to the wider region,
OL,10,Fwith Iran striking its Gulf neighbours
OL,11,Fand Israel launching an offensive in
OL,12,Fsouthern Lebanon and Beirut.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Iran fired missiles into
OL,15,Fthe United Arab Emirates and Bahrain,
OL,16,Fwhile Saudi Arabia said it had
OL,17,Fdestroyed two drones over its oil-rich
OL,18,Feastern region and Kuwait's National
OL,19,FGuard said it had shot down six drones.
OL,21,FWhat has Trump said?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FSpeaking to reporters on Monday night,
OL,8,Fthe US president said: "We are
OL,9,Fachieving major strides towards
OL,10,Fcompleting our military objective -
OL,11,Fsome might say they are pretty much
OL,12,Fcomplete."
OL,14,FHe added: "We're ahead of our initial
OL,15,Ftimeline by a lot."
OL,17,FTrump repeatedly referred to the war
OL,18,Fas an "excursion" and claimed it was
OL,19,F"protecting the world from what these
OL,20,Flunatics are trying to do".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FHe said that Iran's missile capability
OL,8,Fhad been reduced to a fraction of what
OL,9,Fit was and that its navy had been
OL,10,Fdestroyed.
OL,12,F"We are winning decisively," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FIran has effectively stopped tankers
OL,8,Ffrom using the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,9,Fshipping lane between the Persian Gulf
OL,10,Fand the Gulf of Oman ` the gateway to
OL,11,Fthe Indian Ocean ` through which 20%
OL,12,Fof the world's oil is carried. Attacks
OL,13,Fon merchant ships near the strait have
OL,14,Fkilled at least seven sailors,
OL,15,Faccording to the International
OL,16,FMaritime Organisation.
OL,18,FIran launches drones at Saudi Arabia
OL,19,Fand Kuwait
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FIran fired drones towards Saudi Arabia
OL,8,Fand Kuwait early on Tuesday morning.
OL,10,FThe Saudi Defence Ministry said it
OL,11,Fdestroyed drones in the king's oil-
OL,12,Frich eastern region, as the National
OL,13,FGuard in Kuwait confirmed it shot down
OL,14,Fdrones in the country's northern and
OL,15,Fsouthern areas.
OL,17,FIncoming missile sirens sounded across
OL,18,FDubai as well as Bahrain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe United Arab Emirates said on
OL,8,FMonday it had detected 253 ballistic
OL,9,Fmissiles since the conflict began, of
OL,10,Fwhich 233 were destroyed and 18 fell
OL,11,Finto the sea. Two missiles fell on the
OL,12,Fcountry's territory, the country's
OL,13,FMinistry of Defence said.
OL,15,FFour people have been killed, and 117
OL,16,Fothers have suffered minor injuries,
OL,17,Fthe statement said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
