PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe country has also detected 1,440
OL,8,FIranian drones, 81 of which fell
OL,9,Fwithin the country and 1,359 of which
OL,10,Fwere intercepted.
OL,12,FIran's Revolutionary Guard says it
OL,13,Fwill determine when the war ends
OL,15,FThe parliamentary Revolutionary Guard
OL,16,Fsaid on Tuesday that the end of the
OL,17,Fwar will be determined by Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
