PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FSpokesperson Ali Mohammad Naini said
OL,8,Fin a statement published across
OL,9,Fvarious Iranian state media and
OL,10,Fapparently in response to Trump's
OL,11,Fcomments on Monday that "Iran will
OL,12,Fdetermine when the war ends."
OL,14,FOil prices fall back after soaring to
OL,15,Fa four-year high
OL,17,FAn estimated 20% of the world's oil
OL,18,Fsupply has now been disrupted as a
OL,19,Fresult of the conflict in the Middle
OL,20,FEast.
OL,26,@sD@YOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/28
