OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FOil prices soared to nearly $120 a
OL,8,Fbarrel - a four-year high - fuelling
OL,9,Fglobal fears of rising inflation as
OL,10,Fthe escalating conflict entered its
OL,11,Fsecond week on Monday, but hours later
OL,12,Fhad fallen back significantly to below
OL,13,F$90.
OL,15,FBefore the war began, oil was priced
OL,16,Fat around $60-70 per barrel.
OL,18,FConcerns regarding the impact on UK
OL,19,Fhouseholds' bills remain, as energy
OL,20,Fbills are forecast to rise by 10% from
OL,21,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
