PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FTrump commented several times on the
OL,8,Fprice of oil on Monday, seeking to
OL,9,Falleviate concerns about a prolonged
OL,10,Fprice increase.
OL,12,FHe told journalists that any attempt
OL,13,Fby Iran to stop the globe's oil supply
OL,14,Fwould mean it would "get hit at a
OL,15,Fmuch, much harder level".
OL,17,FIsraeli forces target Hezbollah's
OL,18,Ffinancial arm
OL,26,@vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/28
