OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe Israeli military says it has
OL,8,Fcompleted a series of strikes which
OL,9,Ftargeted Hezbollah's financial arm, al-
OL,10,FQard Al-Hasan.
OL,12,FIsrael says Hezbollah uses al-Qard Al-
OL,13,FHasan to finance its military
OL,14,Factivities.
OL,16,FUS behind strike on Iranian school,
OL,17,Finvestigation suggests
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
