CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FA video clip "appears to contradict"
OL,8,FTrump's claim that Iran was
OL,9,Fresponsible for a February 28 strike
OL,10,Fon an Iranian school that killed more
OL,11,Fthan 165 people, investigative group
OL,12,FBellingcat has said.
OL,14,FThe footage shows a Tomahawk cruise
OL,15,Fmissile - which only the US is known
OL,16,Fto possess in this war - falling on a
OL,17,Fbuilding and sending a dark plume into
OL,18,Fthe air. Both Bellingcat and AP
OL,19,Fgeolocated the video to a site near
OL,20,Fthe school.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FSpeaking about the attack on Monday,
OL,8,FTrump claimed many countries had
OL,9,FTomahawk missiles, including Iran.
OL,11,FWhen pressed by journalists on the
OL,12,Fissue, he said: "I just don't know
OL,13,Fenough about it."
OL,15,FHe added that "whatever the report
OL,16,Fshows, I'm willing to live with that
OL,17,Freport".
OL,19,FDefence Secretary Pete Hegseth said
OL,20,Fthe US was investigating what happened.
OL,26,@uD@QO]wD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/28
