OL,14,FAustralia grants asylum to five
OL,15,Fmembers of the Iranian women's
OL,16,Ffootball team
OL,18,FFive members of the Iranian women's
OL,19,Ffootball team have been granted asylum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FThe announcement followed days of
OL,8,Furging by Iranian groups in Australia
OL,9,Fand President Trump for the Australian
OL,10,Fgovernment to help the women, who had
OL,11,Fnot spoken publicly about a wish to
OL,12,Fclaim asylum.
OL,14,FThe players notably did not sing the
OL,15,FIranian anthem before their first
OL,16,Fmatch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/28
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FEarly on Tuesday, police officers
OL,8,Ftransported five of the women from
OL,9,Ftheir hotel in Gold Coast, Australia,
OL,10,F"to a safe location" after they made
OL,11,Fasylum requests.
OL,13,FThere, they met with Home Affairs
OL,14,FMinister Tony Burke and the processing
OL,15,Fof their humanitarian visas was
OL,16,Ffinalised, the minister told reporters
OL,17,Fin Brisbane.
OL,19,FThe women granted asylum were happy
OL,20,Ffor their names and pictures to be
OL,21,Fpublished, he said.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/28
