FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773169064
OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FBurke added that the players wanted to
OL,8,Fmake clear that they were "not
OL,9,Fpolitical activists."
OL,11,FIran's new supreme leader
OL,13,FIran's Assembly of Experts named
OL,14,FMojtaba Khamenei to succeed his
OL,15,Ffather, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, as the
OL,16,Fcountry's new supreme leader,
OL,17,Faccording to state media. Ali Khamenei
OL,18,Fwas killed in US-Israeli strikes last
OL,19,Fweekend.
