OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FMojtaba Khamenei, 56, was not
OL,8,Fimmediately announced on Sunday, after
OL,9,FIsrael and the US threatened to target
OL,10,Fany successor.
OL,12,FPresident Trump had earlier told ABC
OL,13,FNews he wants a say in who comes to
OL,14,Fpower once the war is over. A new
OL,15,Fleader "is not going to last long"
OL,16,Fwithout his approval, Trump added.
OL,18,FCrowds gathered holding Iranian flags
OL,19,Ffor a demonstration in support of
OL,20,FMojtaba Khamenei in Tehran on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/28
