OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,F"The valuable choice of Ayatollah
OL,8,FSeyyed Mojtaba Hosseini Khamenei is a
OL,9,Fmanifestation of the people's will in
OL,10,Fgovernance," Iran's president Masoud
OL,11,FPezeshkian said in a post on X.
OL,13,FConflict escalates in Turkey
OL,15,FNATO air defences have shot down a
OL,16,Fsecond Iranian ballistic missile in
OL,17,FTurkey's airspace, the country said on
OL,18,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/28
