OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,F"We once again emphasise that all
OL,8,Fnecessary measures will be taken
OL,9,Fdecisively and without hesitation
OL,10,Fagainst any threat directed at our
OL,11,Fcountry's territory and airspace," the
OL,12,FTurkish defence ministry said.
OL,14,FIt comes after Turkey deployed six F-
OL,15,F16 jets and air defence systems to the
OL,16,FTurkish-Cypriot part of the divided
OL,17,Fisland of Cyprus to boost its security.
OL,19,FThe statement released on Monday says
OL,20,Fadditional measures would be taken if
OL,21,Fdeemed necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/28
