OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FTurkey maintains some 30,000 troops in
OL,8,Fnorthern Cyprus, which broke away from
OL,9,Fthe Greek south in 1974.
OL,11,FTurkey is the only country to
OL,12,Frecognise the northern administration.
OL,13,FA British air base on Cyprus' southern
OL,14,Fcoastline was hit by a drone last week.
OL,16,FHow did we get here?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/28
