OL,3,CIran fires new attacks at Gulf
OL,4,Ccountries as Trump says war will be
OL,5,C'very soon'
OL,7,FIsrael and the US launched what they
OL,8,Fdescribed as "pre-emptive" strikes
OL,9,Fagainst Iran just before 6.30am on
OL,10,FFebruary 28, which they view as intent
OL,11,Fon acquiring nuclear weapons, shortly
OL,12,Fafter a round of negotiations.
OL,14,FIran denies seeking nuclear weapons,
OL,15,Fand some legal experts have said the
OL,16,Fattack violated international law. The
OL,17,FIslamic Republic has responded by
OL,18,Fstriking Israel and a number of
OL,19,Ftargets in Gulf states allied with the
OL,20,FUS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/28
